The following package should be installed before RainbruRPG is installed:

* rainbrurpg-logger
  + Needed.
  + homepage:
    http://rainbrurpg.sourceforge.net
  + download:
    http://sourceforge.net/projects/rainbrurpg/files/logger/

* Boost.Asio
  + Needed.
  + homepage:
    http://think-async.com/Asio
  + download:
    http://sourceforge.net/projects/asio/files/asio/

* Boost.Filesystem 1.34
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/
